## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not include the latest research findings. The impacts of climate change are complex and multifaceted, and while this report covers significant areas, it may not encompass all possible effects. Additionally, the focus is primarily on general trends and may not reflect specific regional variations in climate change impacts.